cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.DS 

This paper focuses on the detection of Android ransomware using learning-based approaches. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also discusses the use of Machine Learning, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a new detection strategy, which could fall under cs.SE (Software Engineering). Finally, the paper uses data analysis and comparison of different approaches, which could also fit under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
